episodes.title: Talking to Jehovah's Witnesses on trolley duty in Birmingham
episodes.description: In Birmingham on Friday 28th July 2017 having a chat with JW's regarding their doctrines and beliefs, I brought up the subjects of false prophecy and the claim that their organization believes God is guiding and using them, its quite strange really because there are many people who believe similar things but they are usually locked up in mental institutions.
